  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A platformer game where you play as a German Shepherd named Ollie, trapped in his own dreams. Can you pass the main challenge and free Ollie from captivity?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will delight you with pleasant graphics, diverse locations, the ability to improve character characteristics, and dynamic events in locations that will help you not to get bored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your character control skills to confidently overcome any difficulties and easily complete the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pleasant graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character enhancement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic in-game events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique gameplay as a dog</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A platformer game where you play as a German Shepherd named Ollie, trapped in his own dreams. Can you pass the main challenge and free Ollie from captivity?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will delight you with pleasant graphics, diverse locations, the ability to improve character characteristics, and dynamic events in locations that will help you not to get bored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your character control skills to confidently overcome any difficulties and easily complete the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pleasant graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character enhancement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic in-game events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique gameplay as a dog</p></li></ul>",
